{"id":"hananeel","term":"Hananeel","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>God has graciously given, a tower in the wall of Jerusalem (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 3:1\">Neh. 3:1</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 12:39\">12:39</a>). It is mentioned also in <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Jeremiah 31:38\">Jer. 31:38</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Zechariah 14:10\">Zech. 14:10</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Nehemiah 3:1","Nehemiah 12:39","Jeremiah 31:38","Zechariah 14:10"]}